    "betterquesting:10": {
      "autoClaim:1": 0,
      "desc:8": "The Crop Breeder is a new single-block machine that allows players to breed new crops deterministically. It will consume two seeds (the parents), some enriched fertilizer and a catalyst item for material-based plants.\n\r\nThe fertilizer cost is 1000L per tier of the offspring crop + 500L for each start point the new seed will have (it uses the average of the parents).\nSo a 31/31/31 tier 5 offspring would cost 51KL to breed. Ididine, osmianth and stargtatium are all IV recipes, \rTitania is EV, and Bauxia is MV.\n\nBred crops will always have stats that are the average of their parents; breeding two maxed-out crops will always give a maxed-out offspring.\n\r\n§lSuccess chance starts at 50% and increases by 10% for every tier past\nMV, meaning that at ZPM, it’s guaranteed. A failed breed will void the \nparent seeds used.\n\n\n§rYou only need one of the machines for this quest.",
